age/width=480,quality=80,format=auto/media-assets/image/20230610_PDP506.jpg 480w, https://www.economist.com/cdn-cgi/image/width=600,quality=80,format=auto/media-assets/image/20230610_PDP506.jpg 600w, https://www.economist.com/cdn-cgi/image/width=834,quality=80,format=auto/media-assets/image/20230610_PDP506.jpg 834w, https://www.economist.com/cdn-cgi/image/width=960,quality=80,format=auto/media-assets/image/20230610_PDP506.jpg 960w, https://www.economist.com/cdn-cgi/image/width=1096,quality=80,format=auto/media-assets/image/20230610_PDP506.jpg 1096w, https://www.economist.com/cdn-cgi/image/width=1280,quality=80,format=auto/media-assets/image/20230610_PDP506.jpg 1280w, https://www.economist.com/cdn-cgi/image/width=1424,quality=80,format=auto/media-assets/image/20230610_PDP506.jpg 1424w" src="https://www.economist.com/cdn-cgi/image/width=1424,quality=80,format=auto/media-assets/image/20230610_PDP506.jpg" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></figure></section><p class="article__body-text">生育率正在下降到令人担忧的水平，而<a href="https://www.economist.com/leaders/2023/06/01/global-fertility-has-collapsed-with-profound-economic-consequences" data-tegid="0q23hle5umgs3m09inm6ckpfqoj0c6lk">全球人口老龄化、人口减少</a>对经济增长来说是个坏消息。 Apple 的新<a href="https://www.economist.com/leaders/2023/06/06/apples-vision-pro-is-an-incredible-machine-now-to-find-out-what-it-is-for" data-tegid="1kjm56q5gboeo9oqt6h50384453o9u53">耳机</a>可以彻底改变虚拟现实世界，但前提是它能够销售。而且，尽管几十年来一直在下降，但英国<a href="https://www.economist.com/britain/2023/06/03/britons-still-do-like-to-be-beside-the-seaside" data-tegid="fbe1gqc1jssh8pbsd40bievuthi9l7hu">海滨城镇</a>的潮流正在转向。运行时间：26 分钟</p><p class="article__body-text"><iframe height="215" src="https://embed.acast.com/theintelligencepodcast/not-born-yesterday-the-worlds-ageing-population" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></iframe></p><p class="article__body-text">收听： <a href="https://podcasts.apple.com/us/podcast/the-intelligence-from-the-economist/id1449631195">Apple 播客</a>|<a href="https://open.spotify.com/show/12zKAMN